          "tz": 600
        },
        "subject": "LU-8633 osc: check if vmpage is in use in osc_lru_shrink",
        "message": "LU-8633 osc: check if vmpage is in use in osc_lru_shrink\n\nlru_page_busy should always check if the vmpage is in use,\notherwise osc_lru_shrink could evict a page which is read in\nby another thread handling a page fault and waiting on it\nto become up to date.\nEvicting such a page would cause a SIGBUS delivered to the\nthread handling the page fault.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Dongyang <dongyang.li@anu.edu.au>\nChange-Id: I8a9ddcc3a494d0bd8f4c2fe916b3e4efe006d5c6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
